snippet.title: MY FIRST MAP - Doom II: Six Minute Showdown - Ultra-Violence 100%
snippet.description:
Get the map here: https://www.doomworld.com/forum/topic/141816-six-minute-showdown-a-map-with-rhythmic-elements-that-move-to-the-beatmelody/?tab=comments#comment-2740024

To view the map without combat and only the moving elements: https://youtu.be/EGGawjKtlUE

Thanks to: 
- @CammyWritesMusic  for creating Chicago Typography (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zS_VgV1zR3g) and Boston Cream Pie (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=okuToCXp6ow)
- AD_79 for creating Undefined (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q_xUH9G6Ask)

0:00 - Intro
0:41 - Gameplay
8:06 - Doom Builder

Wad: SMS.wad 
Source port: DSDA-Doom 0.27.3 (comp level 9)

This map is played on Ultra-Violence with 100% kills and secrets, pistol start and no saves.

#doom
